                            <strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 2025<br>
                            <strong>Version:</strong> 1.0 (The "Ceramic Frog" Edition)
                        </p>
                        <p class="mt-3">
                            <i class="fas fa-heart text-danger me-2"></i>
                            Made with love, coffee, and a healthy sense of humor by Beloved Websites
                        </p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
